OL,3,CMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,4,CHospital temporarily suspended
OL,6,FMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,7,FHospital are to be temporarily
OL,8,Fsuspended over the weekend due to
OL,9,Fstaff shortages.
OL,11,FThe Southern Health and Social Care
OL,12,FTrust said due to "unexpected staff
OL,13,Fsickness" within obstetrics and
OL,14,Fgynaecology services, they would be
OL,15,F"unable to provide safe medical cover"
OL,16,Fat the Newry site.
OL,18,FCare will be provided at Craigavon
OL,19,FArea Hospital from Friday evening
OL,20,Funtil 9am on Monday to "ensure the
OL,21,Fsafety of women and babies".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
