OL,3,CMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,4,CHospital temporarily suspended
OL,6,FA small number of maternity patients
OL,7,Fcurrently in Daisy Hill will be
OL,8,Ftransferred to Craigavon to continue
OL,9,Ftheir care.
OL,11,FThe trust sincerely apologised for any
OL,12,Fworry or inconvenience caused.
OL,14,FThey added the trust "continues to
OL,15,Fface ongoing medical staffing
OL,16,Fchallenges" within obstetrics and
OL,17,Fgynaecology.
