OL,3,CMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,4,CHospital temporarily suspended
OL,6,FAny women who are concerned should
OL,7,Fphone Craigavon Area Hospital
OL,8,FMaternity Assessment Unit for advice
OL,9,Fon 028 3756 1830.
OL,11,FThe trust will continue to keep the
OL,12,Fsituation under review.
